while you're still here...

04:51.346 --> 04:52.766
"Know that I live on,

04:52.866 --> 04:54.366
"Vibrating to
a different measure

04:54.466 --> 04:57.006
"Behind a thin veil
you cannot see through.

04:57.106 --> 05:00.027
"You will not see me,
So you must have faith.

05:01.227 --> 05:03.687
"I wait for the time when
we can soar together again,

05:03.787 --> 05:05.327
"Both aware of each other.

05:05.427 --> 05:06.887
"Until then,

05:06.987 --> 05:08.727
"live your life to its fullest

05:08.827 --> 05:10.167
