07:42.156 --> 07:44.256
-Yeah.
-MAN: Otherwise it's stealing.

07:44.356 --> 07:49.796
(CHUCKLES) Um, do you think I could
grab some, um, hot popcorn, please?

07:51.116 --> 07:53.116
WOMAN: How long does
'Withnail and I' go for?

07:54.077 --> 07:56.077
OK, great. Thank you.

08:01.437 --> 08:03.017
