08:09.637 --> 08:11.638
Greatest rock band of all time.

08:12.718 --> 08:14.018
You like Radiohead?

08:14.118 --> 08:15.898
Mate, I get the calendar
every year.

08:15.998 --> 08:18.138
Same. Family present.

08:18.238 --> 08:21.358
You know they've got
a, um, jigsaw puzzle too?

08:22.398 --> 08:24.658
