to meet ya, Dom.

10:12.564 --> 10:15.065
-Oh, you too, man.
-Yeah.

10:15.165 --> 10:17.165
Oh, um...

10:18.365 --> 10:20.185
-I'll see you round?
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

10:20.285 --> 10:22.285
Like a rissole!

10:33.006 --> 10:35.046
Hey, we should...

10:40.206 --> 10:42.226
