10:44.326 --> 10:45.986
I don't know!

10:46.086 --> 10:47.746
He was cool,

10:47.846 --> 10:49.227
like me.

10:49.327 --> 10:51.187
You know, he had
the limited edition

10:51.287 --> 10:52.387
Radiohead jigsaw puzzles.

10:52.487 --> 10:55.067
-Wow! That is really cool.
-Yeah.

10:55.167 --> 10:58.907
