you do about me?

11:17.768 --> 11:20.748
No! No, we're far more evolved
than that.

11:20.848 --> 11:22.588
Oh, right, so you
couldn't make a friend,

11:22.688 --> 11:25.389
so you've just come here
to follow me around.

11:25.489 --> 11:28.189
Well, you're the only friend
that I like.

11:28.289 --> 11:29.869
(LAUGHS) That's sad, Dom.

11:29.969 --> 11:31.629
What about Birdie?

11:31.729 --> 11:33.469
Well, she's always working,

11:33.569 --> 11:36.069
because she's a high-flying
businesswoman, you know?

11:36.169 --> 11:37.549
(CHUCKLES) Wow.

