can you do my washing?

12:06.651 --> 12:07.951
Huh!

12:08.051 --> 12:10.191
Um, you can help me hang it out.

12:10.291 --> 12:12.611
Oh. Yeah, look, I...

12:13.691 --> 12:15.631
