share house except I'm the maid.

13:55.377 --> 13:58.037
OK, Mum, we did not ask you
to make breakfast this morning.

13:58.137 --> 13:59.957
And what was that
childish nonsense,

14:00.057 --> 14:01.277
hiding under the sheets?

14:01.377 --> 14:03.358
-We were embarrassed!
-So was I!

14:03.458 --> 14:06.678
